    "millsfield:images_texts": [
      "air niugini",
      "LIMITED\nEDITION\nRONAUTICA COUCTORS\nAIR NUIGINI:\nAirbus Industries: A300B4-203 Airbus:\nConstruction Number:\n134\nRegistration Number: P2-ANG\nAIR NUIGINI _\n_ PX.\ncommenced leasing this Airbus from TRANS\nAUSTRALIA AIRLINES — TN — in November 1984. This airplane was\nVH-TAA with T.A.A. but immediately prior to the AIR NUIGINI lease,\nit had been leased to CONDOR FLÜGDIENST - DF — of Frankfurt.\nwas D-AITA. The initial schedule requires this Airbus to visit Brisbane\nand Sydney in Australia and to Manila (The Philippines) and Singapore\ntwice weekly each. Our photo was taken at Melbourne Airport prior\nto the airplane joining the AIR NUIGINI fleet.\nPhoto: N. Pittaway\nAIRONAUTICA, C/O KOGARAH P.O., NSW 2217 AUSTRALIA\nSTAMP\nHERE\n190285\nPRINTED IN\nAUSTRALIA\nPC30\n2015.166.0038"
    ],
